page.title: 10A CHILD'S DAY : 29:5:85
page.content: 07.40 WOKE UP 08.05 GOT DRESSED 08.10 EAT BREAKFAST 08.15 BRUSH TEETH AND HAIR. READ COMIC 08.30 LEAVE TO GO TO SCHOOL 09.00 MORNING SCHOOL STARTS 10.45 BREAKTIME :SNACK AND PLAY GAMES 11.00 SECOND PART OF SCHOOL STARTS 12.45 GO HOME FOR LUNCH 13.30 SCHOOL STARTS FOR AFTERNOON 15.00 SCHOOL ENDS FOR PUPILS. 15.10 DO HOMEWORK. 15.30 GO GOLFING AT BUGHT PARK 16.25 COME HOME AND WAIT FOR TEA READ MY COMICS 17.30 HAVE MY TEA AND THEN PLAY WITH MY LITTLE SISTER 18.45 MY LITTLE SISTER GOES TO BED 19.00 PLAY TENNIS AND THEN WATCH T.V. 21.00 GET READY FOR BED. 22.00 IN BED AND FALL ASLEEP.
